					<![CDATA[
						 <h1><span>Holy crap thanks for +200! And so quickly, too! :D</span></h1> <hr /> <p>This was super fun to write. Like, insanely fun.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Not&nbsp;to&nbsp;get&nbsp;deep&nbsp;but...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Let's&nbsp;get&nbsp;deep</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>I sort of originally had the idea about my anxiety, since I both crave attention as a writer/actor, but hate being singled out, and am constantly terrified of what others think of me.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Also shouts out to MAFT for being an amazing partner and super talented at both planning ideas, and writing stuff.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
