				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12496767#post-4353544</guid>
				<title>The formatting is intentional please don&#039;t fix it</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12496767/scp-4773-2#post-4353544</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2019 23:17:49 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>MaliceAforethought</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2902864</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Gosh I had a blast collaborating with Henzoid on this. In-universe, it basically represents what happens when a less experienced part of the Foundation &#8212; the Department of Miscommunications &#8212; gets their hands on a genuine bonafide antimeme. Spoiler alert: it ain't good! Out-of-universe, it represents Henzoid coming up to me and saying &quot;here's an idea&quot; and me saying &quot;okay but couldn't they do [xyz]&quot; and him saying &quot;but what if they couldn't&quot; and me going to a dark place very very quickly. Sorry.</p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Image credit:</span> All Henzoid's wonderful work. Aren't they swish?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
